data.title: All Ranked And Registered For 2024 NHSCA High School Nationals
data.meta_description: Registration is set for the 2024 NHSCA High School Nationals. Check out who's headed to Virginia Beach this year.
data.text:
2024 NHSCA High School Nationals goes down this weekend in Virginia Beach. Before the action gets underway, take a look at all the wrestlers who have registered for this loaded championship event. The seeded wrestlers are listed at top of each weight class, and national rankings are included where applicable.
